@node FOREWORD "The Playerģ 5.0A: Foreword"

1. Foreword:
≠≠≠≠≠≠≠≠≠≠≠≠

This little utility was first made just for fun and to my own use. But when
I noticed that there weren't a GOOD Protracker-compatible replay available 
and after I saw a few tries to fix this (ProPacker, Prorunner, etc.) I
decided to give other people a chance to play their Protracker-tunes FAST!

When designing the moduleformat, I also included packing and this 5.0 packing
method is the most efficient I've seen for this purpose.

I also made a converter to make it easier to use PT-modules. It uses Reqtools
and Powerpacker libraries (both by Nico FranÁois) so it can also load
Powerpacked modules. The converter is made as easy as possible to the user.
@endnode

